Privacy Policy for QR Code Maker and Reader App

1. Hello!
Welcome to QR Code Maker and Reader! This Privacy Policy outlines how we handle user data within our app.

2. Camera Permission
2.1 Purpose:
QR Code Maker and Reader App requires access to your device's camera for scanning QR codes.

2.2 Data Collection:
We do not collect, store, or transmit any information obtained through the camera.

3. Scanning History
3.1 Local Storage:
QR Code Maker and Reader saves a history of scanned QR codes locally on your device for your convenience.

3.2 Storage Purpose:
The scanning history is stored solely on your device to provide a record of your QR code interactions within the app.

4. User Consent
4.1 By using QR Code Maker and Reader App, you consent to allowing the app access to your device's camera and the local storage of scanning history for QR code functionality.

5. Security
5.1 Data Security:
While QR Code Maker and Reader App accesses the camera and saves scanning history, no data is shared externally. Your privacy and security remain our top priorities.

6. Updates to Privacy Policy
6.1 We may update this Privacy Policy as needed. Any changes will be effective immediately.

7. Contact Information
7.1 If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy, please contact us at [support@nquila-dev.com].
